ition\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"inParis\", \"from\": 474, \"to\": 481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers said Paris 2024 would be the \\\"greenest ever\\\" Games, working alongside its sponsors towards economic, social and environmental responsibility.\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.727785728863691e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 495}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"greenest ever\\\" Games\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"its sponsors\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"economic, social and environmental responsibility\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But researchers have warned that ice usage during summer Games has reached \\\"extraordinary levels\\\".\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"researchers\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 654}, {\"ngram\": \"ice usage\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 681}, {\"ngram\": \"summer Games\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"extraordinary levels\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report published in the British Journal of Sports Medicine said: \\\"Beyond the financial implications for the local organising committee, this raises environmental concerns, as ice provision requires water and considerable amounts of energy for production and storage.\\\"\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The report\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"the British Journal\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 782}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports Medicine\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the financial implications\", \"from\": 81