effects\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2681}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British athlete, who won gold in the men's individual pursuit cycling at the 1992 Olympics in Barcelona, said: \\\"We have had all the weather - torrential rain going over the Peak District on day one, through to scorching and intense heat and above average temperatures - we have done climate change in a week.\\\"\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 3015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2706, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.999999357612275, \"rank\": 5.639375476470784e-07, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\", \"score\": 0.999849806581704, \"rank\": 0.00015021597457580337, \"text\": \"Barcelona\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barcelona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's individual pursuit cycling\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1992 Olympics\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2796}, {\"ngram\": \"all the weather - torrential rain\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"the Peak District\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"scorching and intense heat\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"average temperatures\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 2973}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3003}, {\"ngram\": \"a week\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the 550-mile ride, Mr Boardman visited different sports clubs leading the way on sustainability, including plans to be net zero by 2029 or gathering volunteers to do conservation work and litter picking.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boardman_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9999999500478237, \"rank\": 3.959474903833859e-08, \"text\": \"Boardman\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boardman_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boardman_High_School\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 550-mile ride\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3041}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports clubs\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3085}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"plans\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3136}, {\"ngram\": \"volunteers\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"conservation work\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3207}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The point of the ride was not just to highlight the issue of climate change and its impact on sport but also to give people hope,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The point\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3239}, {\"ngram\": \"the ride\", \"from\": 3243, \"to\": 3251}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3287}, {\"ngram\": \"climate change\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"its impact\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3320}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3324, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3353}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the projects we visited along the route have shown that we can do this, we can do it together and sport is perfectly placed to lead that change.\\\"\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the projects\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3388}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 3406, \"to\": 3415